## TTupleLike type

Tuple version of ArrayLike.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type TTupleLike<TIndexes extends number, TValue, TLength extends number> = {
    [I in TNeverFallback<TIndexes, number>]: TValue;

    length: TLength;
};
```
